title._content: Piccadilly From Mt. Lofty, South Australia

description._content: Image Description from historic lecture booklet: "In the south, one branch of the Great Dividing Range sweeps westward toward the boundary of Victoria and South Australia. In South Australia a chain of mountains runs northward from the neighborhood of Adelaide and terminates in Filinder's Range."
